properties.content: Input an integer value in "Rule Value" field. Bugsnag will send an alert  after that number of additional occurrences.

Note:  This bugsnag error is showing as reopened.   In order to remove it from Bugsnag review queue, manually adjust the Trigger Type to blank (along with making sure there is a Dev ticket open to handle the issue of course).

Some errors can repeat in bugsnag from release to release, unfortunately.   To ease the pain, let's try to avoid opening duplicate tickets.  

Using the above Bugsnag Duplicate(?) entry link field, try to see if there is already an existing bugsnag with the same error linked to a Veoci Ticket.   If there is, link to the same Veoci Ticket, rather than opening a new one, unless the Linked Veoci Ticket is already Completed/Invalid.  In that case, do open a new one.

Note: sometimes the error *looks* the same, but it is not.  Please make sure you review and make the right decision to create new, or link to existing accordingly.
